  "duration": 95.035,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 1.579,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And all these things",
      "verse": "9:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 1.759,
      "end": 4.592,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "did my father see, and hear, and speak,",
      "verse": "9:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 4.772,
      "end": 8.023,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "as he dwelt in a tent, in the valley of Lemuel,",
      "verse": "9:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 8.203,
      "end": 10.757,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also a great many more things,",
      "verse": "9:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 10.937,
      "end": 13.677,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which cannot be written upon these plates.",
      "verse": "9:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 14.357,
      "end": 17.515,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, as I have spoken concerning these plates,",
      "verse": "9:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 17.695,
      "end": 20.017,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold they are not the plates",
      "verse": "9:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 20.197,
      "end": 24.237,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "upon which I make a full account of the history of my people;",
      "verse": "9:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 24.417,
      "end": 28.179,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the plates upon which I make a full account of my people",
      "verse": "9:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 28.359,
      "end": 30.356,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I have given the name of Nephi;",
      "verse": "9:2",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 30.536,
      "end": 32.997,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so, they are called the plates of Nephi,",
      "verse": "9:2",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 33.177,
      "end": 34.663,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "after my own name;",
      "verse": "9:2",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 34.843,
      "end": 38.001,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and these plates also are called the plates of Nephi.",
      "verse": "9:2",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 38.681,
      "end": 41.746,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But, I have received a commandment of the Lord",
      "verse": "9:3",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 41.926,
      "end": 43.876,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I should make these plates,",
      "verse": "9:3",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 44.056,
      "end": 45.821,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the special purpose",
      "verse": "9:3",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 46.001,
      "end": 50.877,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that there should be a record engraven of the ministry of my people.",
      "verse": "9:3",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 51.557,
      "end": 54.111,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Upon the other plates should be engraved",
      "verse": "9:4",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 54.291,
      "end": 56.752,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "a record of the reign of the kings,",
      "verse": "9:4",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 56.932,
      "end": 59.718,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the wars and contentions of my people;",
      "verse": "9:4",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 59.898,
      "end": 63.195,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so these plates are for the more part of the ministry;",
      "verse": "9:4",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 63.375,
      "end": 67.787,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the other plates are for the more part of the reign of the kings",
      "verse": "9:4",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 67.967,
      "end": 70.939,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the wars and contentions of my people.",
      "verse": "9:4",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 71.619,
      "end": 74.684,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "So, the Lord has commanded me to make these plates",
      "verse": "9:5",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 74.864,
      "end": 76.814,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for a wise purpose in him,",
      "verse": "9:5",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 76.994,
      "end": 78.712,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which purpose I know not.",
      "verse": "9:5",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 79.392,
      "end": 82.039,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But the Lord knows all things from the beginning;",
      "verse": "9:6",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 82.219,
      "end": 83.659,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so, he prepares a way",
      "verse": "9:6",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 83.839,
      "end": 87.136,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to accomplish all his works among the children of men;",
      "verse": "9:6",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 87.316,
      "end": 89.313,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for behold, he has all power",
      "verse": "9:6",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 89.493,
      "end": 91.815,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to the fulfilling of all his words.",
      "verse": "9:6",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 91.995,
      "end": 93.342,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And thus it is.",
      "verse": "9:6",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 93.522,
      "end": 94.358,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Amen.",
      "verse": "9:6",
      "lineIndex": 33
    }
  ]
}